modName: VB - Variant Bodies (A BodySlide Preset) - DELETED
summary: A Slider Preset for BodySlide 2, to get different body-shapes for female NPCs in game.
descriptionHtml:
Ever wander around Skyrim and wonder why all the women are nearly the same shape and size? (and men for that matter, but the mod doesn't address that)
This little Bodyslide Preset aims to fix that by creating a very skiny body model for low weight and a very curvaceous body for high weight.


[b]Requirements:
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE[/url]
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?]BodySlide 2
[/url]
Recommended:
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53996/?]HDT Physics Extention[/url]
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54044/?]HDT Breast and Butt Physics[/url]
-An HDT compatible Skeleton (Bsp. [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/?]Groovtama's Skeleton[/url])
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25259/?]Remodeled Armor for CBBE Bodyslide and TBBP HDT[/url][/b]
or
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12273/?]Caliente's Vanilla Outfits for CBBE[/url]
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32731/?]Patch to use it with extended Sliders[/url]

Credits: Caliante for the awesome Bodyslide Tool
author: Velocirobtor
